casebody.data:
The State of Ohio, Appellee, v. Mullins, Appellant.

[Cite as State v. Mullins (1996), 76 Ohio St.3d 129.]

*130(No. 96-316 — Submitted May 21, 1996 — Decided July 24, 1996.) Alan F. Sedlak, Pickaway County Assistant Prosecuting Attorney, for appellee. • Ralph S. Silvestri, Jr., for appellant. Per Curiam.

We affirm the judgment of the court of appeals for the reasons stated in its decision and judgment entry.

Judgment affirmed.

Moyer, C.J., Douglas, Resnick, F.E. Sweeney, Pfeifer, Cook and Stratton, JJ., concur.
